<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3d7e04c97c276c7f31640ea0235b461760810f51","tid":1536913,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d3bf892deb2abf348b91ea2be1e49817056b14","tid":1536913,"uid":1089,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:18:57.000Z","msg":"好市民係呢度，各位埋黎比D掌聲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OesFUZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOesFUZL.jpg&h=fa154f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:03:40.000Z","msg":"嘩，條撚屌好英勇喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcffe929348f20108f84d95b49498d4ec4d1140","tid":1536913,"uid":208262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:22:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}